## SHUTDOWN -- MANDATORY BEFORE ENDING ANY SESSION

**Every session, no exceptions.** This is as important as startup. If you skip this, the next session starts blind.

**Trigger conditions -- do this when ANY of these happen:**
- User says "wrap up", "that's it", "good night", "end session", or similar
